    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for this awesome ride! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a smooth, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road with you today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles! \u2728",
