    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power distribution through the rear wheels. Recent mechanical attention includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a structural subframe inspection. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a well-damped suspension. A mechanically sound example of an analog performance icon.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
