    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained SUV offers the perfect balance of luxury and dependability. Finished in a deep Midnight Blue, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface scratches one would expect from careful daily use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is appointed with charcoal leather seating that remains supple and supportive, with all power features, dual-zone climate control, and the premium infotainment system functioning flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health; it comes with a fully documented service history, including a recent brake service and a fresh set of all-season tires. It shifts smoothly through all gears and handles the road with quiet confidence. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner, offering a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
