    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures! It\u2019s been well-cared for and still has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019d love for someone to get as much joy out of it as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it!",
      "price": 29500.0,
