    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving S54 inline-six masterpiece. It features individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a functional M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The chassis exhibits sharp turn-in and predictable weight transfer, while the hydraulic steering provides the tactile feedback modern racks lack. Though it displays minor cosmetic wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains tight and the valve clearances are within spec, making this an exceptional performance platform.",
